extendedInfo.description: The NASSP Conference: Ignite 2013 marks a transition to a 21st century learning experience. Everything from the program content to the interactions with colleagues will create the same kind of personalized, participatory learning environment that you, as a school leader, strive to create for your students. Look forward to: ? Engaging and interactive sessions ? Advanced, cutting-edge content from thought leaders in education ? In-depth exchanges for meaningful learning ? Strategies to empower your students to be college and career ready ? Develop a plan to return to school ready to activate innovation ideas. More information is available at www.nasspconference.org.Keywords: NASSP NASSP 2013 Ignite Ignite 2013 NASSP Conference
